      <title>穆迪将英国南部水务公司的评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-s-southern-water-risks-downgrade-to-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级正在考虑将英国公用事业公司南方水务公司的优先债务评级下调至垃圾级，这一最新迹象表明，泰晤士水务公司的困境可能蔓延至英国水务行业的其他领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-s-southern-water-risks-downgrade-to-junk-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
