      <title>英国在工业界抗议下提高北海石油和天然气税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-raises-north-sea-oil-gas-taxes-amid-protest-from-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新政府履行承诺，加强对北海石油和天然气生产商的税收制度，增加暴利税并取消一些投资津贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-raises-north-sea-oil-gas-taxes-amid-protest-from-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
